Your memory reflects two parallel goals: Pantheon as a long-term leverage platform, and Wild Hawg as the nearer-term cash-flow engine.

Those reinforce each other.

* Wild Hawg generates capital.
* Pantheon generates intellectual property, methods, and tooling.
